# CometChat Internship â€“ UI Kit Implementation (React)

This repository contains my implementation of the React UI Kit generated using the CometChat UI Kit Builder as part of the internship task.

---

## ğŸš€ How to Run the Project

1. Clone the repo:
https://github.com/webDevHydra/CometChat-Internship

2. Install dependencies: npm install


3. Create a `.env.local` file (not included in the repo).  
Use your CometChat App credentials:

REACT_APP_COMETCHAT_APP_ID=xxxx
REACT_APP_COMETCHAT_REGION=xxxx
REACT_APP_COMETCHAT_AUTH_KEY=xxxx


Alternatively, refer to the provided `.env.example` file.

4. Start the project: npm start


The app will run at **http://localhost:3000**

